casebody.data: Appeal of OTIS WELD RICHARDSON and EDWARD B. RICHARDSON, Executors under the Will of CATHERINE E. RICHARDSON, deceased. Docket No. 1685. Submitted April 27, 1925; decided May 21, 1925. O. W. Richardson, Esq., for the taxpayer. L. G. Mitchell, Esq., and J. F. Grecuney, Esq., for the Commissioner. Before SteRnhaoen, Trammell, and Love. [NO OPINION]
